text: Ingemar Düring (2 September 1903 - 23 December 1984) was a Swedish Classical Philologist. From 1945 to 1970 he was a professor at Gothenburg University. His most notable work is Aristotle in the Ancient Biographical Tradition ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Swedish philologists Category:University of Gothenburg faculty
